      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just feel like i'm constantly messing everything up for my kids. everything i try to do just ends up making things harder for them or dragging them down with me. i feel like a shadow over the whole house. honestly, i think they'd just be way happier if i wasn't even around to weigh them down all the time.",
